	<description>
		<p>Password Secure encrypts the user's accounts and web sites login data, using a master password.</p>
		<p>Features:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>state-of-the-art AES-256 symmetric-key encryption</li>
			<li>offline storage, using portable files</li>
			<li>automatic backup creation, before updating the stored data</li>
			<li>secure copying and editing of passwords, without revealing them</li>
			<li>automatic clipboard clearing on application exit</li>
		</ul>
	</description>

